= Concept for Investor-backed Upgrade to 10,000 Square Feet =

[[An Idea For Tempe Migration]]: This page proposes an approach for an investor group to purchase a building with HSL as the anchor and preferred tenant using 10,000 ft2 of space.

[[Ten Thousand Foot Layout Concept]]: This page presents a potential layout with HSL having 10,000 ft2 of space in a 15,425 ft2 building.

[[Tempe Migration Financial Analysis]]: Diving in on the numbers behind getting investors interested in buying a commercial property that meets HSL's needs.
